description: The 17 prime powers n = p^w such that d[p^w]^3 > p^w where d = A000005().
comments: For all divisors of the LCM of the terms of this sequence (14515200) the defining relation d[x]^3>x is also satisfied.
example: Differences d[x]^3-x of the 17 entries of this sequence are: 6,5,23,3,1,56,18,109,2,37,184,279,44,384,473,488,307.
author: _Labos Elemer_, Aug 16 2000
